Airhammer and Noctorro had asked Quickstride and Rat Trap about what
they knew of Rodimus, also Silverbolt was urging Kup to step out of
the medical bay as Santon and Bump were urging the Maximals to leave
so that they could get to the operation :)

Is Tuscon heading back to the Ark or is he just driving? Making sure I
know his aim before i post anything for that. I would imagine his
sonar would be enough to get him back to the Ark if he desired, unless
that is down, or I have missed something - I'm still catching up :)
